text: Moonmoon Chakraborty (born 17 August 1993) is an Indian entrepreneur and model. She is a fashion designer and runs her own firm named Style Agent. == Early life and education == She has been honored with many awards like India International Influencer Award 2024, Bollywood Lifestyle Award, Dadasaheb Phalke Award, Bollywood Legend by KCF, Rashtriya Ratna Samman, Bollywood Iconic. She has been given this award by many Bollywood celebrities including singer Kumar Sanu and Padma Shri Udit Narayan. == References == == Other websites == * Moonmoon Chakraborty On Instagram Category:1993 births Category:Living people
